REMARK 
<bibRefCitation author="Perrier" box="[813,969,1319,1346]" firstAuthor="Perrier" pageId="26" pageNumber="283" pagination="1 - 104" refId="ref46247" refString="PERRIER E. 1875. - Revision de la Collection de Stellerides du Museum d'Histoire naturelle de Paris. Reinwald, Paris, 384 p., (also published in: Archives de Zoologie experimentale et generale vol. 4 [1875]: 263 - 449, et vol. 5 [1876]: 1 - 104)." type="book chapter" year="1875">Perrier (1875)</bibRefCitation>
